{"tid":1093902,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A]從零開始的魔王 事前登錄 （魔王係毒撚，睇落唔好玩）","createTime":"2019-04-06T01:43:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-11T07:52:46.000Z","uid":229919,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"327142c87f9bad7726104dd0d594eef257fcfcd2","tid":1093902,"uid":229919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T01:43:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔係Re: 從零開始的異世界XX </span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.qoo-app.com/game/7559/GifVcEmHAzUPXVo3KcKu17Hcvu53QpYo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.qoo-app.com%2Fgame%2F7559%2FGifVcEmHAzUPXVo3KcKu17Hcvu53QpYo.jpg&h=ea755f98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【遊戲介紹】<br />\n這個遊戲你將扮演一個大魔王<br />\n你的目標是打敗其他的大魔王<br />\n你要保證你的種族可以延續下去<br />\n所以你除了要戰鬥外，還要去尋找屬於你的愛情，照顧你的妹妹們<br />\n畢竟，愛は人生の原動力です！ ！<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.qoo-app.com/game/7559/HLWEAsoG35HKiZvABWQKH45KipSxVHji.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.qoo-app.com%2Fgame%2F7559%2FHLWEAsoG35HKiZvABWQKH45KipSxVHji.jpg&h=4f8d41b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【特色玩法】<br />\n1、海量劇情，打造原創IP<br />\n世界混沌動盪，正等待你統御魔族，征服整個大陸，懷春的少女們期待與你相遇，簽下契約，帶來全新的羈絆，現在命運的齒輪將要開始轉動&hellip;被選中的人啊，你準備好了嗎？<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.qoo-app.com/game/7559/kEOkSWG16vHhXV4SYb9fvvhlaWNSkSgD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.qoo-app.com%2Fgame%2F7559%2FkEOkSWG16vHhXV4SYb9fvvhlaWNSkSgD.jpg&h=3854a8a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2、約會戀愛，與女王甜蜜約會<br />\n與神話眾神、精靈、魅魔、人​​類多元角色戀愛互動，隨著公主親密度提升更可解鎖使魔，一步步登上異世界魔族巔峰<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.qoo-app.com/game/7559/bGSBSu1x46Vw9UpkotwzAl30SgfoKb0u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.qoo-app.com%2Fgame%2F7559%2FbGSBSu1x46Vw9UpkotwzAl30SgfoKb0u.jpg&h=945c5f84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n3、經營養成，發展你的永夜城<br />\n統領魔族中心永夜城，你肩負重振威名的使命，現在開始處理政務、資源蒐集、召開宴會來經營壯大永夜城；與此同時，招募惡魔、天使、騎士等魔將加入麾下，解鎖獨特屬性！<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.qoo-app.com/game/7559/EI6EJgF8pNw5BAJLufvDkhnHVjJsgXhL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.qoo-app.com%2Fgame%2F7559%2FEI6EJgF8pNw5BAJLufvDkhnHVjJsgXhL.jpg&h=b81c0dc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n4、頂級立繪，日本知名聲優加盟<br />\n日本頂級CV陣容，花澤香菜、釘宮理惠、佐倉綾音等等傾力獻聲，配合海內外知名畫師精心製作的人物立繪，將角色萌系、禦姐、傲嬌屬性體現得淋漓盡致<br />\n<br />\n事前登錄：<br />\n<a href=\"https://page.heyyogame.com/mw/20190325/?sou=share&amp;fromUser=10156296124588364\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpage.heyyogame.com%2Fmw%2F20190325%2F%3Fsou%3Dshare%26fromUser%3D10156296124588364&d=K4UaoR%2Bzp7qM8XPwf0LBIx3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=0602460c\" target=\"_blank\">https://page.heyyogame.com/mw/20190325/?sou=share&amp;fromUser=10156296124588364</a>"},{"pid":"7f6ec54ebd5761c80da24c891c6b3de40d85f866","tid":1093902,"uid":229919,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T07:18:28.000Z","msg":"推下奬勵先"},{"pid":"d5ec166485d872ba4612c12a5d1dc00a54026445","tid":1093902,"uid":235635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T12:55:30.000Z","msg":"有冇青有玩？"},{"pid":"c997632a6fa4ae1ab5a75b0720201b62b175fec1","tid":1093902,"uid":104133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T08:05:09.000Z","msg":"有無公會可以入？"},{"pid":"d73834038dad2c70138e0f3cf6aab9f4374bf1bd","tid":1093902,"uid":235635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c997632a6fa4ae1ab5a75b0720201b62b175fec1","tid":1093902,"uid":104133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T08:05:09.000Z","msg":"有無公會可以入？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T17:27:45.000Z","msg":"Ching 玩到邊？"},{"pid":"470d843023e5f3c556b9330db1a2db2f20c0766c","tid":1093902,"uid":52013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T07:52:01.000Z","msg":"異世界版叫我官老爺"},{"pid":"267a3fa88c8bdc09704dcb511f25bdc2eff8e8cc","tid":1093902,"uid":52013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T07:52:46.000